{"tid":1468571,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋需要一份聲明","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:23:34.000Z","uid":36088,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8f5e0fdbe549745aef71939f24036c7a15a4c6","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:14:53.000Z","msg":"71立法會，宣讀聲明，成功帶風向令成件事個意義唔同曬<br />\n<br />\n今次機場事件，極需要帶風向<br />\n為成件事定性，為不足之處辯解<br />\n<br />\n民記只係一個整合平台，我哋唔應該靠整合平台寫聲明，因為代表性唔夠，所以應該準備好一份聲明係現場同民記發表<br />\n<br />\n我認為聲明要包括以下內容：<br />\n1. 向受影響旅客致歉<br />\n2. 譴責中共及香港警察派間碟破壞和平示威<br />\n3. 強調香港政府不作為及警黑濫暴為示威活動激化原因<br />\n4. 承認今次行動「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」<br />\n5. 重申5大訴求"},{"pid":"f2cda2d421f9d95a789cc47612885f45689bcb37","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:10.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"123013bf06b8d784f1cb8ca59e8f8026b2905450","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:20.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5d33b4713a13aa2985bb556a15c855a8ce56af09","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"bd697064f167089b504e8fdfde2e1f281aa4f851","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"54351f1aef9739537674b16b380e76444bb99a50","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"fd174d6d50f3f50f9e0e1e6c7c421383a6765a40","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:16:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"2cb61025fe0e822825835af39bbdc254f36b4754","tid":1468571,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"民間記者會應該有準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d868eaed5380fce115af817284b536074ea1818c","tid":1468571,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBczp5z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBczp5z.png&h=ef8f265e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/030750_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F030750_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=a698575a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc9622ce728085d9963561896789a4ac7079f892","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb61025fe0e822825835af39bbdc254f36b4754","tid":1468571,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"民間記者會應該有準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:45.000Z","msg":"我哋唔知民記點寫<br />\n雖然佢哋一向高質，不過寫聲明都係透明d好，咁先有廣範認受性"},{"pid":"964adee96ee8e385e448ecf50a399068a52ce8f3","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d868eaed5380fce115af817284b536074ea1818c","tid":1468571,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBczp5z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBczp5z.png&h=ef8f265e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/030750_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F030750_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=a698575a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:58.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9c949435567a771ffd555a7bc184aa91bdc30054","tid":1468571,"uid":296055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:19:19.000Z","msg":"各位請幫忙分享出去！！！如果你們願意，請幫忙分享以下道歉文章到自己的Facebook,ig,爭取在林鄭講廢話指責我地之前，為811及812中在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉而道歉。並請繼續分享出去！！！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n鑒於這兩天於機場舉行的和平理性機場集會，為各位旅客帶不便，在此，我們真心誠意向各位致歉。<br />\n<br />\nWe would like to sincerely apologize for all the inconvenience caused by the peaceful demonstration at the HK International Airport over the last two days.<br />\n<br />\n我們重申，今次的機場集會，目的為和平理性地引起政府回應及國際關注，希望各位能夠體諒，香港人爭取五大訴求嘅初衷。<br />\n<br />\nOur demonstration aims to peacefully raise the awareness of the global community, as well as response from the HK government on the five demands from the public of Hong Kong. We thank you for your tolerance and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n我們再次向在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉，感謝各位的諒解。<br />\n<br />\nTo all the reporters, ambulance staff, airport staff and affected passengers, we again would like to express oir deepest apology to all the inconvenience and disruptions<br />\n<br />\n感謝所有仍堅持初心嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n一群等待政府回應訴求的香港人"},{"pid":"28b86fd4a9b005b4c9b4a893797b2a013eaca38f","tid":1468571,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:19:23.000Z","msg":"Message to the Free World<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nplease read"},{"pid":"f3eb78731bb8ab01da2d841986d4226e02c62662","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28b86fd4a9b005b4c9b4a893797b2a013eaca38f","tid":1468571,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:19:23.000Z","msg":"Message to the Free World<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nplease read"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:18.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0deeec934441116bebf80517614b96e50eaa8bbb","tid":1468571,"uid":36088,"like